    Introduction
    ~~~~~~~~~~~~

 The Amiga has lots of Bomberman clones already, so why another one?

Well, although some are good, they still lack some of the great
features of the snes Super Bomberman series.  I'm setting out to put
this right !

 This is a demo version, featuring all the death match features with
the player controled as keyboard or CD32 pad. (joysticks will work)


 Improvements from the first version are as follows:

   * Sound.

   * 4 human or CPU players w/ selectable skills.

   * 8 different levels, each with their own features.

   * Skull and time detinators now implemented.

