    Requirements
    ~~~~~~~~~~~~

 Bomber Blaster requires an amiga with around 2 megs of Ram.

An 030 is highly recomended, is it is very slow on an unexpanded A1200.

    Usage
    ~~~~~

 Simply run it from the icon. You will then get more detailed
instructions on how to play the game.


